¿Estás durmiendo?

518
00:39:31,420 --> 00:39:32,472
<i>[ Señor Lee ]</i>

519
00:39:32,472 --> 00:39:33,490
<i>[ Señor Kim ]</i>

520
00:39:35,856 --> 00:39:37,817
<i>[ Señora Ahn ]</i>

521
00:39:41,018 --> 00:39:43,277
<i>Ey, Señor Byun.
